Meet our 10 freshly made drawing tutorials! Now you can draw a lion a swan or even a chibi with our new My Sketchbook update! And there s more good news. We ve created a whole new brush set so you can make more elaborate and detailed drawings. We are constantly working on bringing new experiences to the app. Please don t hesitate to contact us if you find any bugs or want to suggest any art lessons improvements! Let s draw together!
